survey_response.review_text: \"I had approached 'Dental Care center' with my friends suggestion. First, I am very much satisfied with doctor's advice, adhering and flexibility in timings. Results are good and is as expected\
Good guidance and effective treatment. I had visited the clinic for alignment of teeth. The doctor explained to me in detail about the invisible aligners and I’m very happy with the results.

I am old patient  of Dr Nalini, I am a satisfied customer 
I always remember the best treatment given to by Dr Nalini, though I reside in Dharwad I prefer to visit Bangalore/Dr Nalini for any of my dental problems 
I once again convey my sincere thanks to Dr Nalini and the team for the excellent treatment

On enquiry before going to the clinic, Dr. Nalini sent a detailed explanation of the extra caution exercised during these times of Corona Virus, which was extremely useful.
Also, on arrival, extreme care was taken to follow all procedures and the relief on the face of the patient was palpable.

Have been going here since 5th grade for braces. Had 2 premolar extractions, and after removal of braces, not happy with my smile it looks wierd. My face has become extremely flat and ended up with a slight lisp. Also, she had made me wear braces for 6 years when the prescribed time is 3 years, for no good reason and I ended up with cavities after removing them. Would not recommend coming here for braces.

Dr has to be very friendly with the patient... the way she attends the patient with the negative  attitude..
***** *** ***** ** ******* **** ** **** ********* ** *** *********** *** straight away she vll hand over to the juniors widout explaining patient abt the problem..

Consultation was really good, But when it comes to pricing, it is very expensive.

For me to remove three wisdom teeth she quoted 16K, which i guess very high.
I also visited other doctor and charges were very low compared to that.
So i decided to not admit there and get it removed from some other clinic.

I have always written positive and will continue to write the same. 
The services given is the best and so is the rate. A very experienced doctor and someone who has seen thousands of patients. 
To the people whom i recomend, say It's way to costly but you have to realise that with higher amount comes greater service. 
You can't get an apple device in Chinese rates. In case you get it would be fake or grey. 
So its you who has to decide at the end of the day.
Dr Nalini is an excellent doctor who explains the issue patiently and offers an appropriate  treatment
